Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and divided into three teams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first team will head for \NGreen Bit to hand over Caesar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The second team will stay at \Nthe Sunny to guard the ship.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The third team will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.37,0:04:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...destroy the SMILE factory \Nand rescue a samurai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others entered \Na port town - Acacia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:24.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhere they came across living toys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, they walked into a bar to eat something.\NHowever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it go? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! It's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, white!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've missed it again. It's black 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be white this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm running out \Nof luck. This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you wanna do? Do you wanna quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna bet everything\Non whichever color you don't pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play it like real men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Place your bets!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Full of Enthusiasm!\NThe Corrida Colosseum!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pick white, I bet on black, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, white! White!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be black! Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not saying anything. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's white, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That means it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's bl...\N--White!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah?! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look carefully! It's black, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's white.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Stay out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get your ass kicked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDoesn't he have any idea who they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got himself involved, as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!\NHe looks so calm and composed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do I really win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are\Nbut thank you for your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. I just said what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, old man, you look so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're doing is so senseless, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we say "It's black," it's black!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't see anyway so it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, did I trip a big boar or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, could you step aside a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to send those people to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's heavy! So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It left a hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too bad to be blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are many hideous things\Nthat are better unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a Devil Fruit eater?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Devil Fruit is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.87,0:12:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can send a bill for the repairs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, you're so strong! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not tell you that \Nfor the sake of both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you blind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry. Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"For the sake of both of us"?\NIs he extraordinarily infamous or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever he is, he is not an ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, my bag is gone!\N--So is my watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My jacket got stolen, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In broad daylight,\Nwhile there was dust everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man was a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my swords is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Shusui that was here a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The national treasure \Nof the Wano Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! My Shusui...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fairies who took your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.24,0:14:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIs that the name of a group of thieves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairies are fairies.\NAll you can do is laugh it off and let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I laugh it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those invisible fairies are\Nthe guardian deities of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa from ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to turn a blind \Neye to whatever they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if fairies did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sword is the national \Ntreasure of the Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}my{\i0} sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! Somebody gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to challenge you \Nto a duel at some point
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and win the Shusui back for the Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll accept it and defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got too greedy, fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to let you wander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find the thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let anybody \Nhave the national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me! We should go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there are only these guys around,\NI have to take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, they're all out to get attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything up to this big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Wait, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} wait, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the national treasure of\Nthe Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back the national treasure of\Nthe Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He has a strange hairstyle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know my topknot was exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I'm not a child but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're working under Doflamingo, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super{\i0} that's what we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys think\Nyou can mess with the Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Dressrosa and get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna work for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old buddy, why don't you spit it all out -\Neverything we just asked you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember going after a couple of samurai
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know how one got captured\Nand where he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know what SMILE is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know a bit about SMILE?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I don't know the \Nfactory you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.\NEven his man doesn't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell us where people of higher rank are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is too low in rank maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's too busy today -\NI don't know where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been summoned to the Colosseum, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people in this kingdom\Nare heading to the Colosseum today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Corrida Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna see high-ranked \Nofficials, go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.34,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a very big event today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the executives of our \Nfamily should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The very big event that you're talking about is\Nthat {\i1}super{\i0} event?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For whatever reason, Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}\Noffered an unbelievable prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was so surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that delicious meat\Nthat Mingo was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he has something that {\i1}you{\i0} will want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is the prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself for the shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The prize is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:18.66,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE CORRIDA COLOSSEUM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes! The Lightning Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to see it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not for kids to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People will kill each other! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the wanted toy soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen and toys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you will see today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one hell of an event!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king entrusted us\Nwith an extraordinary prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for today's event!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man who died \Nin the War of the Best
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nin Marineford two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a 2nd division commander of\Nthe legendary Whitebeard Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a son of the King of the Pirates -\Nhis name was Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Commandment!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:22:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he could smash through a warship\Nwith his Fire Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and could burn down a town, \Nturning it into hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tremendous power is now \Nreproduced as a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--R-Reproduced?!\N--For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will get this forbidden fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Logia, the most powerful \Ntype of Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No way!\N--That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.43,0:22:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Flare-Flare Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow!\N--I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.16,0:23:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0} won't lie about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Flare-Flare Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:19.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
